        <a href="/ptcl-bill/" class="text-sm bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-primary-600 hover:underline font-medium">PTCL Bill →</a>
        <a href="/dashboard/" class="text-sm bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-primary-600 hover:underline font-medium">Check Bill First →</a>
